high_descs: Pick up the black mug from behind the sink.
Heat up the black mug in the microwave, removing it again.
Turn to face the cabinets above the microwave.
Put the black mug away in the lowest shelf of the right-hand cabinet above the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Heat up a black mug in the microwave to put away in the cabinet above it.

high_descs: Turn and walk toward the sink on the right
Pick up the cup on the counter above the sink
Lift the cup to the microwave
Open the microwave door, place the cup inside, close the microwave door, turn the microwave on, open the door, and remove the cup
Turn all the way around and raise the cup to the cupboard
Open the cupboard door, place the cup on the bottom shelf inside, and close the cupboard door
anns.task_desc: Put a cup back in the cupboard

high_descs: Turn around and make your way to the sink on the left
Pick up the mug from behind the sink
Raise the mug up to the microwave
Heat the mug in the microwave then take the mug out of the microwave
Turn around and go towards the stove, then turn back around and go to the sink and lift the mug up towards the microwave
Put the mug in the left cupboard above the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug into a cupboard
